dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Christian Watson. May I have your name, please?
Hi Christian, my name is Tiffany Lee.
Nice to meet you, Tiffany. Can you please provide me with your policy number for verification purposes?
Sure, it's seven eight nine zero.
Thank you, Tiffany. Could you also confirm the make and model of the vehicle involved in the incident?
It's a two zero one five Toyota Corolla.
Thank you for providing that information. We will process your claim and keep you updated on the status. Is there anything else I can assist you with today, Tiffany?
No, that's all for now. Thank you, Christian.
You're welcome, Tiffany. Thank you for choosing Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day!
